      "title": "Acceptance of postal parcels resumes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The matter has been informed in a media statement issued by Tapalma President Ranjith Ariyaratne.",
        "He emphasized that this will be increased with effect from the first day of August.",
        "Handling of parcels from USA, Netherlands, Israel and Russia has resumed.",
        "Handling of parcels from USA, Netherlands, Israel and Russia has been suspended since last week.",
        "It is noteworthy that the internal postal services were thus suspended due to fuel shortage. (a)"
